\begin{block}{DETECTION}
For this analysis, we assess whether a traditional social network community detection approach will find the covert group.
\begin{enumerate}
\item divide the synthesized data set into time intervals
\item during each time interval, compute the optimal community structure using the fast-greedy heuristic
\item score based on persistent group structure, decaying over time
\end{enumerate}
